reviewText: I thank God for this mentorship series by Juanita Bynum! I am watching again for the second time!

All I can say is know the truth and the truth will make you free.. Awesome Woman of God..Each dvd will have you to re-examine  yourself and to a self check in your spirit absolutely love it...There needs to be more real anointed mothers like Juanita Bynum that teach with love and from the heart and, have a sense of humor.

I was extremely pleased with my purchase. It arrived on time and it was in excellent shape. I was a little nervous because of the price and thought I was going to receive a cheap VCR dubbed DVD but it wasn't.  I will definitely purchase more things from them.
